				<span class="command">npm install</span>
				<span class="app">-g grunt-cli</span>
			</p>
		</div></p>
        <p>In order to run tests and jshint, execute the following command:</p>
        <p><div class="shell">
			<p class="line">
				<span class="prompt">$</span>
				<span class="app">grunt</span>
			</p>
		</div></p>

