			<li><a href="https://developers.google.com/chrome/apps/docs/developers_guide" target="_blank">Chrome Hosted Apps</a></li>
			<li><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/Apps/Build/Manifest" target="_blank">Firefox Open Web Apps</a></li>
		</ul>
